Mangalore Refinery & Petrochemicals
Ltd. (MRPL) , a unit of India’s biggest energy explorer, offered to sell
high-speed diesel and vacuum gasoil for loading in May from New
Mangalore port on India’s west coast, according to documents
sent to potential buyers.  Details of the offers are as follow:  Oil & Natural Gas Corp. (ONGC) , India’s largest energy explorer,
